title: #124: No Restrictions with John Paul Rice
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another insane episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode Sam goes really deep with Film Producer and all-round bad ass, John Paul Rice from No Restrictions Entertainment. We go deep- so buckle up as we discuss the dark arts! Check out JPR's No Restrictions Entertainment's films on Vimeo.
https://vimeo.com/norestrictions
Check them out on twitter as well at @Norestrictions!
Thank you for all of your support!
